Sneak preview of tomorrow’s @theretaility feature on @createcultivate founder @jaclynrjohnson. (Spoiler alert: Her taste in home furnishings is as good as her taste in investments.) Photos by @emilymalan for TheRetaility.com.

Weekend plans?! Here’s a peek at @createcultivate founder @jaclynrjohnson’s backyard in Silver Lake. After years spent hustling, Johnson is finding more balance in her day-to-day. “I kept telling my husband, ‘I’ll chill when the company sells,’” she remembers. “I just wanted to do right by our shareholders and everyone. When the company sold, I became a different person. A hundred percent. I was able to relax more.”

Read and see more at TheRetaility.com.

Words by @lindzischarf.
Photos by @emilymalan.

Visit TheRetaility.com to peek inside the homes, hearts, and minds of California creatives.
